123
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:44,280
And they, of course, said, yes.

124
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:48,640
So I went every day over to my sister's house.

125
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:50,200
And that's how I got hooked up with them.

126
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,400
I would go and say, well, I want

127
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:54,280
to be involved so I went and I joined.

128
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:55,880
And that's what happened.

129
00:09:55,880 --> 00:10:00,640
But there was nothing or anything for us to do.

130
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:02,480
I was going to ask, can you tell me a little bit

131
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:06,360
