132
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:08,000
Well, I met Doc.

133
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:11,000
Doc, you been the one play the piano.

134
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,160
No, no, Janelle.

135
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:14,480
Janelle, you been the play the piano.

136
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:17,240
We would have singing.

137
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:19,480
And we had our little brother, then,

138
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,000
Mr. Was Gerald.

139
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,320
When the Gerald.

140
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:24,360
He was a brother at that time.

141
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,600
He had a little brother.

142
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:28,240
For a little while, he was our president, for not long.

143
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,040
For not long.

144
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:32,160
And we would meet every day and we would go pick it like our

145
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:32,840
Janelle said.

146
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:37,120
It was only a few of us, a handful of people that participated

147
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:39,280
