175
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:57,640
We was unlawful guests.

176
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:59,960
We were undesirable guests.

177
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:05,760
We was trespassing.

178
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:08,800
And if we didn't leave, we would be carried to jail.

179
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:09,840
And that's what happened.

180
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,960
They carried us to jail.

181
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:11,480
Yes.

182
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:16,000
And we was also arrested by a black deputy.

183
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:16,680
Who was named?

184
00:12:17,640 --> 00:12:20,080
DJ Johnson.

185
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:26,240
Which to me, when he put us in that car,

186
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:32,000
I think that really was the hurting part of the whole day,

187
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:39,080
was when he came in and snatched us and told us that we were on the rest.

188
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:42,480
I would imagine he would have been one of the first black deputies.

189
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,120
Oh, no.

190
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:45,000
Oh, no.

191
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:52,200
And I just looked because I grew up knowing him, knowing him,

192
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:56,800
